"title": "6147: deceit, practice of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6147: deceit, practice of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Deceit is condemned by God as an attempt to deny his sovereignty and his revelation of himself.</p>\n<h2>Deceit is forbidden by God</h2>\n<h3>Condemnation of deception in general</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:11\">LEV 19:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:22\">PRO 12:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:28\">PRO 24:28</a></p>\n<h3>False witnesses condemned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:16\">EXO 20:16</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:20\">DEU 5:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:17\">PRO 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:5\">PRO 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:9\">PRO 19:9</a></p>\n<h3>False measures prohibited</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:35\">LEV 19:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:13\">DEU 25:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:1\">PRO 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:10\">PRO 20:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:11\">MIC 6:11</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual deception condemned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:16\">TIT 1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:14\">MAL 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:27-Matt23:28\">MAT 23:27–23:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:46\">LUK 6:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:21\">ROM 2:21</a></p>\n<h2>Deception must not be found in the people of God</h2>\n<h3>God's people must not practise deceit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:1\">1PE 2:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job27:4\">JOB 27:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:4\">PSA 24:3–24:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:2\">PSA 32:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:13\">ZEP 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:24\">JHN 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:8\">1CO 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:25\">EPH 4:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:9\">COL 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:10\">1PE 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:5\">REV 14:5</a></p>\n<h3>Christian leaders in particular must not deceive</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:2\">2CO 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:12\">2CO 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:17\">2CO 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:3-1Thess2:5\">1TH 2:3–2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:8\">1TI 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:7\">TIT 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>God's people warned against being deceived</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:6\">EPH 5:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:8\">JER 29:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:10\">1CO 6:9–6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:33\">1CO 15:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:7\">GAL 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:8\">COL 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3\">2TH 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:7\">1JN 3:7</a></p>\n<h2>Deceit results in God's judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:6\">PSA 5:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:16\">DEU 25:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:23\">PSA 55:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:118\">PSA 119:118</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:17\">PRO 20:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:6\">PRO 21:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:8-Jer9:9\">JER 9:8–9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:9\">EZK 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:9-Acts5:10\">ACT 5:9–5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:8\">REV 21:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:27\">REV 21:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:15\">REV 22:15</a></p>",
